From CARTER EDWARD A Subject Re SQUIDS and Dealers In article writes stuff chopped Here is the part that concerned The HG and those shop personel that were not busy with customers went back out where said HG members fired up their rides and did the obligatory reving up of those At this point one decided to see how much rubber a Katana could deposit in the SQUIDS I thought to BUT I was appalled that the salesdroids manager not only condoned this behavior but encourged it to the point were they were betting how long he could keep it up and egged him on to pull a wheely as he rode off onto a busy street around rush THe girl that was riding pillion on another bike seemed rather hormonal about this display and urged her pilot to quickly catch The others followed making sure there Kerkers could be heard as well as Um you gotta understand these salesdroids as you call They look at it this way burn lotsa tire make lotsa I'm sure s he knew how stupid the HG Would you seriously stop them from burning off a seasons worth of tire The SQUIDS probably would buy Metzelers or some good low profile tire Them droids sure a sneaky bastards Regards University of Toronto Computer Engineering PowerUsersGroupChairman ' I'm taking a ride with my best DoD